'''Andy Amadi Okoroafor numukinnyi''' wa firime [[Nijeriya|wo]] muri [[Nijeriya|Nigeriya]] nkumuvugizi wa TED.  Azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa film ya ''Relentless ya'' 2010.  Usibye gutanga icyerekezo, ni umwanditsi, producer numuyobozi wubuhanzi. Niwe washinze sitidiyo yo guhanga 'Clam'.

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 8 Gashyantare 1966 i Bauchi, mu majyaruguru ya [[Nijeriya]]. Yari afite umwaka umwe igihe intambara yatangiraga i Biafra. Nyuma yaje kwimukira i Paris mu [[Bufaransa]] maze akora nk'umuyobozi ushinzwe ubuhanzi mu kwamamaza, imideli n'amashusho y'indirimbo. Ni na TED-Mugenzi. 

== Umwuga ==
Mu [[Bufaransa]], Okoroafor yamaze imyaka 5 yubuhanzi ayobora amashusho yindirimbo , kuva kuri alubumu kugeza ku mashusho yindirimbo. Yashinze sitidiyo yo guhanga yitwa 'Clam' na 'Clam magazine' mu 1999.  Iki kinyamakuru gisohoka kabiri mu mwaka mu [[Buyapani]], [[Amerika]], [[Uburayi]], na [[Berezile]].  Mu imurikagurisha rya 2017, yayoboye igitaramo ''show Never Surrender'', i M. Bassy i Hamburg, mu [[Budage]]. Muri iki gitaramo harimo gufotora no kwerekana amashusho murukurikirane, ''Aphrike Yinshi'' . Hamwe nuruhererekane, yakoranye na mugenzi we bafotora hamwe nuwakoze firime, Andrew Dosunmu. 

Mu mwaka wa 2010, Okoroafor yakoze filime ''Relentless'', filime ye ya mbere.  Mu Kwakira 2010, iyi filime yatoranijwe mu iserukiramuco rya sinema ryabereye i Londres, ryerekanwa ku ya 6 Ukuboza 2010 mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Afurika ryabereye i Port Harcourt ku nshuro ya mbere muri [[Afurika]]. 

